    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Lead Enrichment Pipeline\n\nWhat this workflow does:\n1. Runs every hour\n2. Reads new leads from Google Sheets\n3. Filters unprocessed leads (status = \"new\")\n4. Enriches each lead with company data via API\n5. Calculates a lead score\n6. Routes by score: Hot (50+) vs Nurturing\n7. Syncs to separate Airtable tables\n8. Updates Google Sheets with sync status\n9. Sends summary to Slack\n\nRequired sheet columns:\nname | email | company | company_domain | source | status\n\nTo test: add rows with status = \"new\" to your sheet,\nor run with the pinned demo data.",
        "width": 440,
        "height": 440,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "a1b0c001-0001-4000-8000-000000000012",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [120, -40]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Lead Scoring Logic\n\nCompany Size:\n- 500+ employees: +30 pts\n- 100-500: +20 pts\n- 20-100: +10 pts\n\nIndustry (high-value):\n- Tech / Finance / Healthcare / SaaS: +25\n- Other: +10\n\nData Quality:\n- Has LinkedIn: +10\n- Has Phone: +10\n- Has Revenue: +15\n\nThreshold: score 50+ = Qualified",
        "width": 300,
        "height": 360,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "a1b0c001-0001-4000-8000-000000000013",
      "name": "Sticky Note1",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
